# Upstream component versions. Single source of truth for the whole repo.
#
# Bumping a version:
#   1. Edit the value below.
#   2. For Go-module-pinned components (GAIE), also update controller/go.mod
#      to the same version and run `cd controller && go mod tidy`.
#   3. Run `make verify-versions` — it regenerates shared/types/versions.generated.ts
#      and checks go.mod is in sync.
#
# Consumers:
#   - Makefiles:  include this file (KEY=VALUE is valid Make syntax).
#   - Shell:      `set -a; source versions.env; set +a`.
#   - Go:         injected via -ldflags at build time (see controller/Makefile).
#   - TypeScript: codegen produces shared/types/versions.generated.ts.

GAIE_VERSION=v1.5.0

# Dynamo upstream omits the v-prefix in chart tarball names and image tags
# (e.g. dynamo-platform-1.1.1.tgz). Sites that need a git tag prepend "v"
# at the use site (see providers/dynamo/Makefile, providers/dynamo/config.go).
DYNAMO_VERSION=1.1.1
